Text:
These girls are actually triplets and "former" MFC models. They now have their own site... http://www.sensual3plets.com/

They are actually quite nice, have chatted with them a couple of times.

An explanation,

They are still on MFC, but their common account where closed by MFC - so now they have separate accounts.
Avoid the the screens - Kaspersky detected malware / trojan loader: Trojan-Downloader.Java.OpenConnection.dc
